Steps.Message: This is UK Power Networks. Due to a safety issue on our electricity network, we may need to switch off some power in your local area. We do normally contact our customers in advance, but as this is for emergency work and in the interest of public safety, we're unable to provide you with much notice. It is a possibility that your power will not be affected by this, if you would like more information call us on 08003163105.

We became aware of this power cut at 13:40. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
